Brazil Preparing Draft Measure to Improve Ethanol Investment

-- B y   M a r i o   S e r g i o   L i m a
-- 
2011-07-27T23:28:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-27/brazil-preparing-draft-measure-to-improve-ethanol-investment.html
The Brazilian government is
preparing a draft measure to faciliate investment in ethanol and
stimulate the growth of plants manufacturing the product,
Minister for Mines and Energy Edison Lobao told reporters today
in Brasilia.  The measure should be published in 10 days, he said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Robin Stringer at 
 rstringer@bloomberg.net  